{"tid":478424,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"［巴打心聲］外型黎講港男真係大部分都係柒既","createTime":"2017-11-24T05:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T14:39:04.000Z","uid":51507,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ac8be66d0791110e8cebb6a60c76cad5c61a1891","tid":478424,"uid":51507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"有時出街都覺得港男大部分都係又矮又毒又柒<br />\n就算先天不足都可以外表穿著搭救呀<br />\n但係事實就係連穿著都有陣柒味 唔係亂9咁著就係扮到韓仔十足但係又要扮得肉酸<br />\n唔係話個個都要打扮到好靚先出街 但係起碼唔好成陣柒味走出黎 比人順眼既感覺先阿<br />\n唔怪得成日比港女話港男唔掂 d人又成日話溝唔到女<br />\n真正見得人既港男1成人都唔知有冇 希望你係個1成人啦<br />\n結論港台日韓外表打扮黎講<br />\n日＞＝韓＞港＝台<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/130802_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F130802_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=29c029c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c0bba29bd468b656b103ea3f8f28377bc8b7cf9","tid":478424,"uid":43983,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T05:11:44.000Z","msg":"抽水最緊要快狠準<br />\n你講果啲講左十幾年啦<br />\n拾人牙慧"},{"pid":"543b8fb709e2af33bf334076640e993ae69075fc","tid":478424,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽水最緊要快狠準<br />\n你講果啲講左十幾年啦<br />\n拾人牙慧</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到"},{"pid":"a38d096ef9d67a6ce54f94e743c3e0dabb1d3075","tid":478424,"uid":9387,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"日<br />\n無撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18a5f5afb71a93dd2b72f7e3a68557aa6827b03","tid":478424,"uid":13885,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T12:38:44.000Z","msg":"去韓國走一轉啦 大部分都樣衰 但香港男仔個樣起碼是是正正"},{"pid":"d2bbd411a75c81cf25faeec37f863d6db59f466a","tid":478424,"uid":72827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"好悶"},{"pid":"c04b8c1614535c0472d5996ad2169b6480